3f1800567f2eb5","tid":1613611,"uid":133495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。"},{"pid":"80b8fb57b8adb83caa969177556aa4eea88f4810","tid":1613611,"uid":215717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"Physics老師話擋RFID錫紙夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4594c22694673866671a77b0db98b0bce54e93","tid":1613611,"uid":215924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5380f84c059014889ecb94a70b9fe533b3126e04","tid":1613611,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbc28db473bddb4ddfaa3c64217032f8c57e892","tid":1613611,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfdb4fb5799b0c247764f9e098e0bfc09d166868","tid":1613611,"uid":35831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"總有啲膠係乾得好快嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"唔撚會有暴徒用熱熔膠呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"好似有隻膠叫快乾膠又叫三秒膠<br />\n未用過，唔知係咪乾得真係咁快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"快乾膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錫紙都 ok <br />\n唔信你試下用嚟包住八達通用電話拍下"},{"pid":"7275ee3d11520e3da4a218177cb1337ffee2c5dd","tid":1613611,"uid":68756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c804e727f6dd84e86bfd5e719f6430a122675c3b","tid":1613611,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset